data.description:
Welcome to this charming two-story townhome with a finished basement, nestled in a cared-for community boasting a
pool and an unbeatable location close to shopping, military bases, and the picturesque Palmer Park with its inviting
hiking trails! Step inside to discover the inviting living room, complete with a cozy stone fireplace, leading to a spacious
kitchen and dining area. The kitchen showcases brand-new countertops, all appliances, and ample cabinet space.
Upstairs, retreat to the master bedroom with its own bath, along with a second master bedroom and another full bath
for convenience. The lower level is designed as a studio apartment, featuring a second living area, an additional *nonconforming* room perfect for guests or an office, and another bathroom. Don't let this meticulously maintained home
slip away— Schedule your viewing today!
